{"tid":1694753,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"注意!! 共識!! 以後大家出黎麻煩要有「3個準備」","createTime":"2019-11-05T09:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T09:38:03.000Z","uid":294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f19ee7df6606169ab39d2fa004cc6ff31431bba","tid":1694753,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"和理非定勇都要注意<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 帶野</span> </strong><br />\n帶乜野自己諗, 唔好得個人淨係唱歌, 你知前線要乜野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 搵D 野做唔好齋企</span></strong><br />\n做乜野自己諗或到時討論, 如果有人齋企, 麻煩搵人D 邀請佢一齊做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3. 捉到鬼 / 藍C / 撕紙狗 / 影大頭狗, 一律當狗論</strong></span><br />\n唔好再講私了, 而係「還X」, X 係乜麻煩大家睇新聞手足失去左D咩<br />\n還X 時, 所有左膠同記一律唔可以接近, 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「一齊爬山, 一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71877ab665abd6374e9f44b09d03c1da5e982f6","tid":1694753,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f19ee7df6606169ab39d2fa004cc6ff31431bba","tid":1694753,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:30:40.000Z","msg":"和理非定勇都要注意<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 帶野</span> </strong><br />\n帶乜野自己諗, 唔好得個人淨係唱歌, 你知前線要乜野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 搵D 野做唔好齋企</span></strong><br />\n做乜野自己諗或到時討論, 如果有人齋企, 麻煩搵人D 邀請佢一齊做野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3. 捉到鬼 / 藍C / 撕紙狗 / 影大頭狗, 一律當狗論</strong></span><br />\n唔好再講私了, 而係「還X」, X 係乜麻煩大家睇新聞手足失去左D咩<br />\n還X 時, 所有左膠同記一律唔可以接近, 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「一齊爬山, 一齊努力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-